sequenceDiagram
    actor A as Administrator
    participant FE as React<br/>AdminUsersPage
    participant API as DRF<br/>AdminUserListView
    participant SER as AdminUserSerializer
    participant Perm as IsAdmin
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    A->>FE: Enter search query (email, name)
    FE->>API: GET /api/accounts/admin/users/?search=john
    API->>Perm: has_permission(request)
    Perm-->>API: Allowed (Admin role)
    API->>DB: CustomUser.objects.filter(Q(email__icontains) | Q(first_name__icontains))
    DB-->>API: Matching users across all tier DBs
    API->>SER: AdminUserSerializer(users, many=True)
    SER-->>API: Serialized user list with roles and status
    API-->>FE: 200 OK {users: [{id, email, role, is_suspended}, ...]}
    FE-->>U: Display filtered user table
